title: Apt. Guide v.2
author: XCstar
pages:
#- YOAHTL APARTMENT§0
§0GUIDE BOOK§0
§0
§0Version 2.0§0
§0
§0Managed by XCstar.§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0Turn to page 2 for FAQ.
#- FAQ§0
§0
§0Q: How do I claim an apartment?§0
§0A: Replace room sign with your name and room number, then lock your door.§0
§0
§0Q: How do I lock my apartment door?§0
§0A: Type /ctr and hit door with some stone.
#- 1 - INTRO§0
§0
§0Welcome to New Yoahtl City's public housing!§0
§0
§0All newfriends without a house are allowed one free apartment.§0
§0
§0Please ask the manager, XCstar, if you have any questions.
#- 2 - RULES§0
§0
§0-Apt. tenants are allowed to privately reinforce blocks within their apartment such as doors, chests, etc.§0
§0
§0-The walls, ceilings, and floor are owned by Yoahtlan govt. and may NOT be modified without permission.
#- 2 - RULES (2)§0
§0
§0Tenant eviction will occur if: §0
§0 -They have been inactive for 3 days after move in. This is an IMMEDIATE eviction.§0
§0 -They have been inactive 5 days. You will be given a 3 day notice period before eviction.
#- 3 - RULES (3)§0
§0
§0 -Eviction will occur if you break apt. or city rules 2 or more times§0
§0
§0-Improper move in will result in an ineligible apartment claim.§0
§0
§0-Co-tenants can live in same unit if agreed upon mutually.
#- 3 - APT. INFO§0
§0
§0These apts. are designed as a place for newfriends to stay as they get familiar with the city.§0
§0
§0We encourage apt. use as you gain armor/XP,§0
§0materials, explore the nation and get familiar with other citizens.
#- 3 - APT. INFO (2)§0
§0
§0-Use the lobby minecart for quick access to upper floors. Get in and out to use.§0
§0
§0-Drop down quickly to the lobby using the water drop. 
#- 3 - APT. INFO (3)§0
§0
§0-Each unit comes with a private obsidian garage. Garage entry is to the right of the apts. Main St. entry. §0
§0
§0-Reinforce garage doors to your own group for use. Open with levers, plates, or buttons.
#- 4 - GENERAL INFO§0
§0
§0Nation: Yoahtl§0
§0City: New Yoahtl City§0
§0(NYC)§0
§0
§0Our govt. is lead by an Alcuahtl with multiple elected councillors.§0
§0
§0Other Yoahtl towns include Southshire and Hypercube.
#- 5 - DISCORD§0
§0
§0Join us on Discord! Discord is our central communication hub that uses text and voice chat for all purpose communication. §0
§0
§0Ask a citizen for an invite to the Discord page.
#- We hope you enjoy your time here in New Yoahtl City!
#- 